        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3589416479" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1614219420880207533">The author&apos;s background in foreign policy and civil wars gives him a rather interesting perspective on the end of the US Civil War, that brings our history into focus. While the story of the end of the war and Reconstruction is more complex than one book can handle, Winik points out how much more badly the aftermath of the war could have gone, but didn&apos;t. Highly recommend</span>
  <span id="freeText1614219420880207533" style="display:none">The author's background in foreign policy and civil wars gives him a rather interesting perspective on the end of the US Civil War, that brings our history into focus. While the story of the end of the war and Reconstruction is more complex than one book can handle, Winik points out how much more badly the aftermath of the war could have gone, but didn't. Highly recommend</span>
